---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="How Rwote handles your data">
  <Header />
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-stone max-w-none space-y-6 text-secondary">
      <p>Last updated: April 16, 2026</p>
      
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary">Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect information you provide directly, including:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Email address (for account creation)</li>
        <li>Notes and tags you create</li>
        <li>Usage data to improve our service</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary">How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use your information to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Provide and maintain the service</li>
        <li>Sync your notes across devices</li>
        <li>Improve user experience</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary">Data Storage</h2>
      <p>Your notes are stored securely using Supabase. We never sell your personal information or note content to third parties.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary">Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use essential cookies for authentication and service functionality. We do not use tracking or advertising cookies.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary">Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You can export or delete your data at any time by contacting support.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary">Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions? Email us at <a href="mailto:privacy@rwote.com" class="text-accent hover:underline">privacy@rwote.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
